    "description": {
      "value": "<p>After summoning your astral arms using @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.fAibWIlBW7I5kFuf]{Arms of the Astral Self}, you can use them to make unarmed strikes.</p>\n<p>Your astral arms have the following qualities:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>They are considered a Monk weapon and use your @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.TMeKDQLocSb3loVv]{Martial Arts} die for damage.</li>\n<li>Your reach is 5 feet greater than normal.</li>\n<li>You can use <strong>Wisdom </strong>in place of your Strength or Dexterity modifier for the attack and damage rolls, and their damage type is force.</li>\n</ul>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note:Â </em><em>You will need to manually change the damage done by this feature at higher levels.</em></p>\n</section>",
